title: About
text: The North American Aquatic Energy Density Toolbox contains data on energy densities of fish and other aquatic organisms collected across the North America. The data helps researchers and managers understand ecosystem health and food web dynamics.

title: North American Aquatic Energy Density Toolbox
text:
Welcome to the the North American Aquatic Energy Density Toolbox (NAAEDT).
This toolbox helps researchers and managers understand ecosystem health and food web dynamics for aquatic ecosystems.
There are several different functions on the website and they include the toolbox, data templates, and data entry forms.
